item.title: Rink Runner Script!
item.dc:creator: @wetodded wetodded
item.description:
@wetodded wrote:

[quote=“yoyoyo989, post:1, topic:13928”]Well here it is,but I must warn you though its hard to click to the next level,and to send your score,but good luck with it anyways!
[scar]//Rink Runner Script
//My 2 Script
//By:yoyoyo989
program runner;
begin
repeat
clickmouse(363,222,true);
sleep(5);
clickmouse(231,168,true);
sleep(5);
clickmouse(223,280,true);
sleep(5);
clickmouse(435,208,true);
sleep(5);
clickmouse(479,236,true);
wait(5);
clickmouse(473,378,true);
wait(20)
until(false);
end.[/scar][/quote]
